sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant API as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as TrainJob Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller
    participant Scheduler as Volcano Scheduler<br/>Gang Scheduling
    participant Pods as Training Pods<br/>Launcher + Workers
    participant Storage as S3/HuggingFace<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Metrics as Progression Tracker<br/>RHOAI

    Note over User,Metrics: Flow 1: TrainJob Creation
    User->>API: kubectl apply TrainJob<br/>TLS 1.3 + User Auth
    API->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-*<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>API: Validation OK
    API->>Controller: Watch event<br/>TrainJob created
    Controller->>API: Create JobSet<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>API: Create PodGroup (Volcano)<br/>TLS 1.3
    Controller->>API: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>RHOAI Extension

    Note over JobSetCtrl,Pods: Flow 2: Training Execution
    JobSetCtrl->>API: Create Jobs/Pods
    Scheduler->>API: Watch PodGroup
    Scheduler->>Pods: Schedule all pods<br/>All-or-nothing
    Pods->>Storage: Download dataset<br/>HTTPS + AWS IAM
    Pods->>Storage: Download model<br/>HTTPS + HF Token
    Pods->>Pods: Inter-pod communication<br/>TCP (NCCL/MPI/gRPC)<br/>NetworkPolicy allowed

    Note over Controller,Pods: Flow 3: Progression Tracking (RHOAI)
    Controller->>API: List pods in JobSet<br/>TLS 1.3
    API-->>Controller: Pod IPs
    loop Every 30s (configurable)
        Controller->>Pods: GET /metrics:28080<br/>HTTP (NetworkPolicy)
        Pods-->>Controller: JSON metrics<br/>{progressPercentage, loss, step}
        Controller->>API: Update TrainJob annotation<br/>trainer.opendatahub.io/trainerStatus
    end

    Note over Pods,User: Flow 4: Completion
    Pods->>Storage: Save checkpoint<br/>HTTPS
    Pods->>API: Job Complete
    Controller->>API: Update TrainJob status<br/>Succeeded/Failed
    API-->>User: TrainJob status update
